    <text>
        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p><bibl><ptr target="#boardman-hayes1973"/>, p. <citedRange>84</citedRange> n. <citedRange>2187</citedRange> (ph., dr.)</bibl>;
                    <bibl><ptr target="#IGCyr"/> <citedRange>004200</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
               <ab>
                   <lb n="1"/><milestone unit="fragment" n="a"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>ᾶς <w lemma="δεκάτα">δεκάτας</w> τᾶ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied> 
                   <persName type="divine" ref="#Demeter"><name nymRef="#Δαμάτηρ"><supplied reason="lost">Δάματ</supplied><milestone unit="fragment" n="b"/><unclear>ρ</unclear>ι</name></persName> <g type="punct">⋮</g> 
                   <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθ<unclear>ε</unclear>̄<supplied reason="lost">κε</supplied></w> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>                    
	 </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Untel</supplied> a consacré sur la dîme à Demeter <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">So-and-so</supplied> dedicated from the tithe to Demeter <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p><supplied reason="subaudible">Il tale</supplied> ha dedicato dalla decima a Demetra <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p><foreign xml:lang="grc">τᾶς δεκάτας</foreign> should be rather a gen. sing. 'from the tithe' than an acc. plur., for this word is usually only a singular.</p>
	<p>This graffito is the only clear instance of a tithe for Demeter. <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr00380</ref> might be another one, <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr003910</ref> is less clear.</p>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
